data.Name: Native Daughters
data.Bio: Native Daughters ~ Denver, CO Instrumental Progressive Metal - Post Metal Denver’s Native Daughters aren’t five guys who work at the same office, realized they all liked Isis, then decided to get together one weekend and jam. There were no record store flyers, no Craigslist ad, and certainly no “management” or marketing plan involved. As Mustangs And Madras ended, most of the band reformed as Native Daughters in 2010, later completing the lineup with guitarist Justin Hackl as his previous band–Only Thunder, met a similar fate.
